{"tid":1686393,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(氣餒手足入)一場夢令我重燃呢場抗爭運動的熱情","createTime":"2019-11-01T05:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T01:38:18.000Z","uid":178800,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a9fc64219b67dbd09eac635fbf2ddefb37e5cc24","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"首先，利申番我係和理非無上過前線<br />\n因為家庭工作種種問題一直無勇氣<br />\n尤其近期popo大舉濫捕，真係驚比人拉<br />\n然後尋晚就發左場夢<br />\n夢入面我成為了一名前線<br />\n明知full gear都唔夠popo砌<br />\n明知出去就有機會被捉到被毒打<br />\n明知會犧牲前途會有好幾年係監倉度過<br />\n果種有去無回既忐忑不安同恐懼<br />\n真係好撚真實呀<br />\n我想係度再一次向咁多位勇武講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地既付出我地無唔記得，亦唔會被白費<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">三千手足被捕</span></span>，佢地被虐打被失蹤被性暴力，大好青春花係監獄度，出到黎因為案底好多工都做唔到，一諗起呢度，我地就絕不能放棄<br />\n踏入十一月，勇武同和理非唔可以再互屌<br />\n請大家回想起初心，六月一直叫緊既口號<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分化不割席</span></span>係方針係方向<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山各有各做</span></span>係實踐係行動<br />\n因為我地有同一目標同一理想<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n齊上齊落煲底相見<br />\n香港人反抗<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be44002898813f5de7f1b88aa6d1e020a2e45e36","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"勇武點樣行動我地唔會干預<br />\n無論點都支持<br />\n至於我地和理非<br />\n都好多野可以做<br />\n二百萬人數就係我地既後盾<br />\n必須做好長期抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">將抗爭融入生活</span><br />\n比林奠知道一直呼籲社會各界一齊止暴制亂就係一個笑話<br />\n由始至終暴亂源頭就係佢同埋popo<br />\n我地要令社會各界無論黃藍中立都要明白<br />\n真正可以止亂就係要令呢個港共跪低<br />\n文宣，twitter戰，捐錢，支持黃店經濟圈&hellip;"},{"pid":"6efd67265230bdc30be7e33f3e4d1179a643b6a7","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"用&quot;甴近平&quot;代替&quot;推&quot;"},{"pid":"2f32be5009f35d1a08955919ddc859de1bfb8b2f","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"fb501034051170ecd2715782980af66eabcd0a2b","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:06:02.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"89f3589d74f124485bb4787808d9520b5676268f","tid":1686393,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"甴曱近"},{"pid":"eae682bfb1d48514e376d65a5400316cd97f548f","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"3853d88369c95cb6d6f3589dcbe917ff6aaa53dc","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"297dbe998cd6a110f2f70192cf3207da19565198","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"寫得咁好都無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6df516550cfbe319a078fb69c3750d03c6f254","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"4cebdb438d6bc09296069a5f8d43a55dc7e20997","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"4a376473c4185c834a0e0b32e48b85ab0eb22a14","tid":1686393,"uid":285117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"72c4f1607248c6f204d41cc8b8a5417b3dc9305b","tid":1686393,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"容易無限支持前線<br />\n做乜都支持"},{"pid":"ac008ae9b6e33eee4ab162b3fcf2554993417eeb","tid":1686393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72c4f1607248c6f204d